### Traveloop API Test Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}
@tripId = {{createTrip.response.body.id}}

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@traveloop.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### 3. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@traveloop.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Get Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Create Trip
# @name createTrip
POST {{baseUrl}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Japan Adventure",
  "startDate": "2026-10-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-10-15T00:00:00Z",
  "description": "Two weeks exploring Tokyo and Kyoto",
  "isPublic": true
}

### 6. Get All Trips
GET {{baseUrl}}/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Add Stop to Trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/trips/{{tripId}}/stops
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cityName": "Tokyo",
  "country": "Japan",
  "startDate": "2026-10-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2026-10-08T00:00:00Z",
  "orderIndex": 0
}

### 8. Search Mock Cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/cities?q=Tokyo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
